    <lb n="5"/>Φιλοξένου καὶ <add place="supralinear"><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/> ἐγγυω<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μένου</unclear>  </add> Ἡλιοδώρου τοῦ Κανδάνου ἀμφοτέρων <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Περσῶν</unclear> τῆς <expan>ἐπιγο<ex cert="high">νῆς</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="6"/>περὶ τῶν διεστ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αμέν</supplied>ων. συνχωρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οῦσ</unclear>ιν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Θερμο</unclear>ῦθις καὶ Φιλόξενος 

